Safran Is Ready to Adapt to Avoid Thales Overlap, Investir Says

-- B y   H e a t h e r   S m i t h
-- 
2011-02-26T09:58:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-26/safran-is-ready-to-adapt-to-avoid-thales-overlap-investir-says.html
  Safran SA  “isn’t hostile to finding
a more rational way to manage our defense activities” in areas
where there is overlap with rival  Thales SA , weekly newspaper
 Investir  reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Jean-Paul
Herteman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
